{"word":"χρυσίον","slug":"χρυσίον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>χρυσίον, ου, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χρυσός\">χρυσός</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dim.\">dim.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χρυσός\">χρυσός</a></el><b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> the precious metal known as <b>gold <a href='B:530 3:12'>1 Cor 3:12</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:650 9:4'>Hb 9:4</a>.</b> W. focus on refined state <b><a href='B:670 1:7'>1 Pt 1:7</a>; <a href='B:730 3:18'>Rv 3:18</a>; <a href='B:730 21:18'>21:18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘object made of gold or decorated with gold’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> personal gold adornment, <b>gold ornament(s), jewelry <a href='B:610 2:9'>1 Ti 2:9</a>; <a href='B:670 3:3'>1 Pt 3:3</a>; <a href='B:730 17:4'>Rv 17:4</a>; <a href='B:730 18:16'>18:16</a>.</b> The two last <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ perh.\">perh.</a> <b>gold trappings. <p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> coined gold, money <a href='B:510 3:6'>Ac 3:6</a>; <a href='B:510 20:33'>20:33</a>; <a href='B:670 1:18'>1 Pt 1:18</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> <b>open plaza <a href='B:730 21:21'>Rv 21:21</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:χρύσεος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:χρυσοδακτύλιος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}